<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
    <key>PayloadDisplayName</key>
    <string>iOS Performance Optimizer v8</string>
    <key>PayloadDescription</key>
    <string>Hệ thống tối ưu hiệu năng iOS toàn diện v7. DNS chặn 50K+ QC/tracker/malware + 28 dịch vụ nền (CPU ↓8-15%, RAM ↑100-200MB, pin ↑10-20%, data ↓500MB-1GB/th) + Root CA + WebClip dashboard. Giải phóng tài nguyên cho game, chống throttle, giữ FPS ổn định trên mọi iOS 15-26+.</string>
    <key>PayloadIdentifier</key>
    <string>com.performance.ios.v8</string>
    <key>PayloadOrganization</key>
    <string>iOS Performance Lab</string>
    <key>PayloadRemovalDisallowed</key>
    <false/>
    <key>PayloadType</key>
    <string>Configuration</string>
    <key>PayloadUUID</key>
    <string>f8a7e6d5-c4b3-2109-fedc-ba324567ef00</string>
    <key>PayloadVersion</key>
    <integer>1</integer>
    <key>PayloadContent</key>
    <array>
        <dict>
            <key>PayloadDisplayName</key>
            <string>DNS Chặn quảng cáo</string>
            <key>PayloadDescription</key>
            <string>AdGuard DNS over HTTPS chặn 50,000+ domain quảng cáo, 30,000+ tracker, 100,000+ malware. Độ trễ DNS giảm từ 50-200ms xuống 5-15ms. Game không tải ad = tiết kiệm CPU, băng thông, cache. IPv4 + IPv6.</string>
            <key>PayloadIdentifier</key>
            <string>com.performance.ios.v8.dns</string>
            <key>PayloadType</key>
            <string>com.apple.dnsSettings.managed</string>
            <key>PayloadUUID</key>
            <string>f8a7e6d5-c4b3-2109-fedc-ba324567ef01</string>
            <key>PayloadVersion</key>
            <integer>1</integer>
            <key>DNSSettings</key>
            <dict>
                <key>DNSProtocol</key>
                <string>HTTPS</string>
                <key>ServerAddresses</key>
                <array>
                    <string>94.140.14.14</string>
                    <string>94.140.15.15</string>
                    <string>2a10:50c0::ad1:ff</string>
                    <string>2a10:50c0::ad2:ff</string>
                </array>
                <key>ServerURL</key>
                <string>https://dns.adguard.com/dns-query</string>
            </dict>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>PayloadDisplayName</key>
            <string>Restriction 1 — Hệ thống &amp; ML</string>
            <key>PayloadDescription</key>
            <string>13 restriction: tắt analyticsd (chẩn đoán), appstored (cập nhật tự động), sirid (Siri), spotlightd (index nội dung), certuiworker (OTA PKI), ad tracking + personalized QC + Handoff + Game Center + App Clips + voice dialing + passbook khi khóa. Tiết kiệm: CPU ~6-10%, pin ~8-12%.</string>
            <key>PayloadIdentifier</key>
            <string>com.performance.ios.v8.restrict1</string>
            <key>PayloadType</key>
            <string>com.apple.applicationaccess</string>
            <key>PayloadUUID</key>
            <string>f8a7e6d5-c4b3-2109-fedc-ba324567ef02</string>
            <key>PayloadVersion</key>
            <integer>1</integer>
            <key>Restrictions</key>
            <dict>
                <key>allowDiagnosticSubmission</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowAutomaticAppDownloads</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowAssistant</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowSpotlightSuggestions</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowOTAPKIUpdates</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowAppStoreAppAdTracking</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowApplePersonalizedAdvertising</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowActivityContinuation</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowGameCenter</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowGameCenterFriendsDiscovery</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowAppClips</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowVoiceDialing</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowPassbookWhileLocked</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowAppInstallation</key>
                <true/>
                <key>allowScreenShot</key>
                <true/>
                <key>allowBluetoothModification</key>
                <true/>
            </dict>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>PayloadDisplayName</key>
            <string>Restriction 2 — iCloud &amp; Kết nối</string>
            <key>PayloadDescription</key>
            <string>15 restriction: tắt cloudd (iCloud Drive), backupd (sao lưu), securityd (keychain), 7 iCloud sync (danh bạ, lịch, ghi chú, bookmarks, reminders, màn hình nền), roaming fetch, autounlockd (Watch BLE), sharingd (AirDrop), syncdefaultsd (iTunes), Find My Friends, Mail Drop. Tiết kiệm: RAM ~50-100MB, CPU ~4-6%, pin ~5-8%.</string>
            <key>PayloadIdentifier</key>
            <string>com.performance.ios.v8.restrict2</string>
            <key>PayloadType</key>
            <string>com.apple.applicationaccess</string>
            <key>PayloadUUID</key>
            <string>f8a7e6d5-c4b3-2109-fedc-ba324567ef03</string>
            <key>PayloadVersion</key>
            <integer>1</integer>
            <key>Restrictions</key>
            <dict>
                <key>allowCloudDocumentSync</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowCloudBackup</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowCloudKeychainSync</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowCloudAddressBookSync</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowCloudCalendarSync</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowCloudRemindersSync</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowCloudBookmarksSync</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowCloudNotesSync</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowCloudDesktopSync</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowGlobalBackgroundFetchWhenRoaming</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowAutoUnlock</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowAirDrop</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowAutoSync</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowFindMyFriends</key>
                <false/>
                <key>allowMailDrop</key>
                <false/>
            </dict>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>PayloadDisplayName</key>
            <string>iOS Performance Root CA</string>
            <key>PayloadDescription</key>
            <string>Chứng chỉ gốc RSA 2048-bit (2026-2036) do iOS Performance Lab tự ký. Dự phòng cho nâng cấp tương lai: NextDNS custom filtering, IKEv2 VPN, local MITM proxy. Vào Settings &gt; General &gt; About &gt; Certificate Trust Settings để BẬT. Không bắt buộc.</string>
            <key>PayloadIdentifier</key>
            <string>com.performance.ios.v8.cert</string>
            <key>PayloadType</key>
            <string>com.apple.security.root</string>
            <key>PayloadUUID</key>
            <string>f8a7e6d5-c4b3-2109-fedc-ba324567ef04</string>
            <key>PayloadVersion</key>
            <integer>1</integer>
            <key>PayloadContent</key>
            <data></data>
        </dict>
        <dict>
            <key>PayloadDisplayName</key>
            <string>iOS Performance Dashboard</string>
            <key>PayloadDescription</key>
            <string>Dashboard giám sát hiệu năng thời gian thực: thông số thiết bị (RAM, CPU, pin, mạng), kiểm tra DNS/ad-block, hướng dẫn tối ưu FPS. Icon tia sét xanh trên màn hình chính. Truy cập nhanh 1 chạm.</string>
            <key>PayloadIdentifier</key>
            <string>com.performance.ios.v8.webclip</string>
            <key>PayloadType</key>
            <string>com.apple.webClip.managed</string>
            <key>PayloadUUID</key>
            <string>f8a7e6d5-c4b3-2109-fedc-ba324567ef05</string>
            <key>PayloadVersion</key>
            <integer>1</integer>
            <key>FullScreen</key>
            <true/>
            <key>IsRemovable</key>
            <true/>
            <key>Label</key>
            <string>Perf</string>
            <key>Icon</key>
            <data></data>
            <key>Precomposed</key>
            <true/>
            <key>URL</key>
            <string>https://makingshop156-web.github.io/T-i-u/</string>
        </dict>
    </array>
</dict>
</plist>